# Cursor Rules for Anh Tho Spa Project

## Project Overview
This is a full-stack spa booking management system built with React (TypeScript) frontend and Node.js/Express backend.

## Code Standards
- Always write code in English
- Use TypeScript for frontend code
- Use JavaScript for backend code
- Follow React best practices
- Use functional components with hooks
- Follow RESTful API conventions

## File Structure
- `/client` - Client-facing pages and components
- `/admin` - Admin dashboard pages and components
- `/staff` - Staff portal pages and components
- `/backend` - Express.js API server
- `/components` - Shared components
- `/services` - Shared services

## Database
- MySQL database using Sequelize ORM
- Database schema defined in `db.txt`
- Models in `/backend/models`

## Important Notes
- Always maintain type safety with TypeScript
- Use proper error handling
- Follow existing code patterns
- Test API endpoints before committing

